raftClone page. </span></p>\n<p><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-44-1.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-380744 aligncenter" src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-44-1.jpg" alt="" width="1048" height="442" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-44-1.jpg 1048w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-44-1-300x127.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-44-1-768x324.jpg 768w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-44-1-1024x432.jpg 1024w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-44-1-510x215.jpg 510w" sizes="(max-width: 1048px) 100vw, 1048px" /></a></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Clicking on the MySQL login link will take you to the following page, where you need to hit Enter on the selected Clone.</span></p>\n<p><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-45.jpg"><img class="wp-image-380745 size-full aligncenter" src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-45-e1556285463863.jpg" alt="" width="791" height="189" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-45-e1556285463863.jpg 791w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-45-e1556285463863-300x72.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-45-e1556285463863-768x184.jpg 768w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-45-e1556285463863-510x122.jpg 510w" sizes="(max-width: 791px) 100vw, 791px" /></a></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This will take you to the final SQL-Admin page, where you can</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> directly manage your Clones database.</span></p>\n<p><a href="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-46.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-380746 aligncenter" src="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-46.jpg" alt="" width="1394" height="898" srcset="https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-46.jpg 1394w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-46-300x193.jpg 300w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-46-768x495.jpg 768w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-46-1024x660.jpg 1024w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-46-1080x696.jpg 1080w, https://updraftplus.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/New-Project-46-510x329.jpg 510w" sizes="(max-width: 1394px) 100vw, 1394px" /></a></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We are sure you will enjoy using this new feature and hope the extra functionality makes your experience cloning a site that little bit better.</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Be sure to let us know any feedback you may have in the comment section below. </span></p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com/updraftclone-release-new-sql-admin-feature/">UpdraftClone release new SQL-Admin feature</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus</a>. <a href="http://updraftplus.com">UpdraftPlus - Backup, restore and migration plugin for WordPress.</a></p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:72:"https://updraftplus.com/updraftclone-release-new-sql-admin-feature/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:67:"https://updraftplus.com/updraftclone-release-new-